quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  19,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  19,1,Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-'Ayyyn-Saaad
  19,2,( yeh ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani ka bayan ( hai jo is ne ) apne bande zikria par ( ki thi )
  19,3,jab unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ko dubi aawaz se puraka
  19,4,( aur ) kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar meri haddiyan burhapay ke sabab kamzor hogayi hain aur sir ( hai ke ) burhapay ( ki wajah se ) shola maarny laga hai aur ae mere perwar-digaar mein tujh se maang kar kabhi mahroom nahi raha
  19,5,aur mein apne baad apne bhai bundon se darta hon aur meri biwi banjh hai to mujhe apne paas se aik waris ataa farma
  19,6,jo meri aur aulaad Yaqoob ki meeras ka maalik ho. aur ( ae ) mere perwar-digaar is ko khush atwaar banaiyo
  19,7,ae zikria hum tum ko aik larke ki basharat dete hain jis ka naam yahya hai. is se pehlay hum ne is naam ka koi shakhs peda nahikiya
  19,8,unhon ne kaha perwar-digaar mere haan kis terhan larka hoga. jis haal mein meri biwi banjh hai aur mein burhapay ki intahaa ko poanch gaya hon
  19,9,hukum howa ke isi terhan ( hoga ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne farmaya hai ke mujhe yeh aasaan hai aur mein pehlay tum ko bhi to peda krchka hon aur tum kuch cheez nah they
  19,10,kaha ke perwar-digaar mere liye koi nishani muqarrar farma. farmaya nishani yeh hai ke tum sahih وسالم ho kar teen ( raat din ) logon se baat nah krsko ge
  19,11,phir woh ( ibadat ke ) hujray se nikal kar apni qoum ke paas aeye to un se isharay se kaha ke subah vsham ( khuda ko ) yaad karte raho
  19,12,ae yahya ( hamari ) kitaab ko zor se pakdae raho. aur hum ne un ko larakpan mein danai ataa farmai thi
  19,13,aur apne paas shafqat aur pakizgee di thi. aur parhaizgaar they
  19,14,aur maa baap ke sath neki karne walay they aur sarkash aur nafarman nahi they
  19,15,aur jis din woh peda hue aur jis din wafaat payen ge aur jis din zindah karkay uthaye jayen ge. un par salam aur rehmat ( hai )
  19,16,"aur kitaab ( quran ) mein maryam ka bhi mazkoor karo, jab woh apne logon se allag ho kar mashriq ki taraf chali gayeen"
  19,17,to unhon ne un ki taraf se parda karliya. ( is waqt ) hum ne un ki taraf apna farishta bheja. to un ke samnay theek aadmi ( ki shakal ) ban gaya
  19,18,maryam bolein ke agar tum parhaizgaar ho to mein tum se khuda ki panah maangti hon
  19,19,unhon ne kaha ke mein to tumahray perwar-digaar ka bheja howa ( yani farishta ) hon ( aur is liye aaya hon ) ke tumhe pakeeza larka bakhson
  19,20,maryam ne kaha ke mere haan larka kyonkr hoga mujhe kisi bashar ne chuva taq nahi aur mein badkaar bhi nahi hon
  19,21,( farishtay ne ) kaha ke yuhin ( hoga ) tumahray perwar-digaar ne farmaya ke yeh mujhe aasaan hai. aur ( mein usay isi tareeq par peda karoon ga ) taakay is ko logon ke liye apni taraf se nishani aurzarya rehmat aur ( meharbani ) bunun aur yeh kaam muqarrar hochuka hai
  19,22,to woh is ( bachay ) ke sath haamla hogyin aur usay le kar aik daur jagah chali gayeen
  19,23,phir dard zeh un ko khajoor ke tanay ki taraf le aaya. kehnay lagen ke kash mein is se pehlay mar chukti aur bholi bisri ho gayi hoti
  19,24,is waqt un ke neechay ki janib se farishtay ne un ko aawaz di ke ghumnaak nah ho tumahray perwar-digaar ne tumahray neechay aik chashma jari kardiya hai
  19,25,aur khajoor ke tanay ko pakar kar apni taraf hilaoo tum par taaza taaza khjorin jhar parrin gi
  19,26,to khao aur piyo aur ankhen thandhi karo. agar tum kisi aadmi ko dekho to kehna ke mein ne khuda ke liye rozay ki minnat maani to aaj mein kisi aadmi se hargiz kalaam nahi karoon gi
  19,27,phir woh is ( bachay ) ko utha kar apni qoum ke logon ke paas le ayen. woh kehnay lagey ke maryam yeh to tunay bura kaamkiya
  19,28,ae Haroon ki behan nah to tera baap hi bad atwar aadmi tha aur nah teri maa hi badkaar thi
  19,29,to maryam ne is larke ki taraf isharakiya. woh bolay ke hum is se ke goad ka bacha hai kyonkr baat karen
  19,30,bachay ne kaha ke mein khuda ka bandah hon is ne mujhe kitaab di hai aur nabi banaya hai
  19,31,aur mein jahan hon ( aur jis haal mein hon ) mujhe sahib barketkiya hai aur jab taq zindah hon mujh ko namaz aur zakaat ka irshad farmaya hai
  19,32,aur ( mujhe ) apni maa ke sath naik sulooq karne wala ( banaya hai ) aur sarkash o badbakht nahi banaya
  19,33,aur jis din mein peda howa aur jis din mron ga aur jis din zindah karkay uthaya jaoon ga mujh par salam (o remat ) hai
  19,34,yeh maryam ke betay eesa hain ( aur yeh ) sachhi baat hai jis mein log shak karte hain
  19,35,khuda ko sazawar nahi ke kisi ko beta banaye. woh pak hai jab kisi cheez ka iradah karta hai to is ko yahi kehta hai ke hoja to woh hojati hai
  19,36,aur be shak khuda hi mera aur tumhara perwar-digaar hai to isi ki ibadat karo. yahi seedha rasta hai
  19,37,phir ( ahal kitaab ke ) firqoun ne baahum ikhtilaafkiya. so jo log kafir hue hain un ko barray din ( yani qayamat ke roz ) haazir honay se kharabi hai
  19,38,woh jis din hamaray samnay ayen ge. kaisay suneney walay aur kaisay dekhnay walay hon ge magar zalim aaj Sarih gumraahi mein hain
  19,39,aur un ko hasrat ( o afsoos ) ke din se dra-o jab baat Faisal kar di jaye gi. aur ( behat ) woh ghaflat mein ( parre hue hain ) aur imaan nahi laatay
  19,40,hum hi zameen ke aur jo log is par ( baste ) hain un ke waris hain. aur hamari hi taraf un ko lootna hoga
  19,41,aur kitaab mein ibrahim ko yaad karo. be shak woh nihayat sachey paighambar they
  19,42,jab unhon ne apne baap se kaha ke abba aap aisi cheezon ko kyun pujte hain jo nah sunen aur nah dekhen aur nah aap ke kuch kaam aa saken
  19,43,abba mujhe aisa ilm mila hai jo aap ko nahi mila hai to mere sath ho jiyay mein aap ko seedhi raah par chala dun ga
  19,44,abba shetan ki parastish nah kijiye. be shak shetan khuda ka nafarman hai
  19,45,abba mujhe dar lagta hai ke aap ko khuda ka azaab a pakray to aap shetan ke saathi ho jaien
  19,46,is ne kaha ibrahimkiya to mere mabodon se bur-ghashta hai? agar to baz nah aeye ga to mein tujhe sangsar kardoon ga aur to hamesha ke liye mujh se daur hoja
  19,47,ibrahim ne salam alik kaha ( aur kaha ke ) mein aap ke liye apne perwar-digaar se bakhshish maanguu ga. be shak woh mujh par nihayat meharban hai
  19,48,aur mein aap logon se aur jin ko aap khuda ke siwa puraka karte hain un se kinara karta hon aur apne perwar-digaar hi ko poukaron ga. umeed hai ke mein apne perwar-digaar ko pukaar kar mahroom nahi rahon ga
  19,49,aur jab ibrahim un logon se aur jin ki woh khuda ke siwa parastish karte they unn se allag hogaye to hum ne un ko Ishaq aur ( Ishaq ko ) Yaqoob bakhshay. aur sab ko paighambar banaya
  19,50,aur un ko apni rehmat se ( bohat si cheeze ) inayat kee. aur un ka zikar Jameel bulandkiya
  19,51,aur kitaab mein moose ka bhi zikar karo. be shak woh ( hamaray ) bargzida aur paighambar marsal they
  19,52,aur hum ne un ko tor ki dahni janib puraka aur baatein karne ke liye nazdeek bulaya
  19,53,aur apni meharbani se unn ko unn ka bhai Haroon paighambar ataakiya
  19,54,aur kitaab mein asmayl ka bhi zikar karo woh waday ke sachey aur hamaray beje hue nabi they
  19,55,aur apne ghar walon ko namaz aur zakaat ka hukum karte they aur apne perwar-digaar ke haan pasandeeda ( o bargazeedah ) they
  19,56,aur kitaab mein adrees ka bhi zikar karo. woh bhi nihayat sachey nabi they
  19,57,aur hum ne un ko onche jagah uttha liya tha
  19,58,yeh woh log hain jin par khuda ne apne payghambaroon mein se fazlkiya. ( yani ) aulaad aadam mein se aur un logon mein se jin ko Nooh ke sath ( kashti mein ) sawaarkiya aur ibrahim aur Yaqoob ki aulaad mein se aur un logon mein se jin ko hum ne hadaayat di aur bargzidakiya. jab un ke samnay hamari ayatain parhi jati theen to sjday mein gir parte aur rotay rehtay they
  19,59,phir un ke baad chand nakhlf un ke janshin hue jinhon ne namaz ko ( chore diya goya usay ) kho diya. aur khwahisaat nafsaani ke peechay lag gay. so anqareeb un ko gumraahi ( ki saza ) miley gi
  19,60,haan jis ne tauba ki aur imaan laya aur amal naik kiye to usay log bahisht mein daakhil hon ge aur un ka zara nuqsaan nahkiya jaye ga
  19,61,( yani ) bahisht javedani ( mein ) jis ka khuda ne apne bundon se wadakiya hai ( aur jo un ki aankhon se ) posheeda ( hai ). be shak is ka wada ( naiko karon ke samnay ) anay wala hai
  19,62,"woh is mein salam ke siwa koi behooda kalaam nah sunen ge, aur un ke liye subah vsham ka khana tayyar hoga"
  19,63,yahi woh jannat hai jis ka hum apne bundon mein se aisay shakhs ko waris banayen ge jo parhaizgaar hoga
  19,64,aur ( firshton ne paighambar ko jawab diya ke ) hum tumahray perwar-digaar ke hukum siwa utar nahi satke. jo kuch hamaray agay hai aur peechay hai aur jo un ke darmain hai sab isi ka hai aur tumhara perwar-digaar bhoolnay wala nahi
  19,65,( yani ) aasman aur zameen ka aur jo un dono ke darmain hai sab ka perwar-digaar hai. to isi ki ibadat karo aur isi ki ibadat par saabit qadam raho. bhala tum koi is ka hum naam jantay ho
  19,66,aur ( kafir ) ensaan kehta hai ke jab mein mar jao ga tokiya zindah karkay nikala jaoon ga ?
  19,67,kiya ( aisa ) ensaan yaad nahi karta ke hum ne is ko pehlay bhi pedakiya tha aur woh kuch bhi cheez nah tha
  19,68,tumahray perwar-digaar ki qasam! hum un ko jama karen ge aur shaitano ko bhi. phir un sab ko jahannum ke gird haazir karen ge ( aur woh ) ghutnon par giray hue ( hon ge )
  19,69,phir har jamaat mein se hum aisay logon ko khech nikalen ge jo khuda se sakht sar kashi karte they
  19,70,aur hum un logon se khoob waaqif hain jo un mein daakhil honay ke ziyada Laiq hain
  19,71,aur tum mein koi ( shakhs ) nahi magar usay is par guzarna hoga. yeh tumahray perwar-digaar par lazim aur muqarrar hai
  19,72,phir hum parhaiz garon ko nijaat den ge. aur zaalmon ko is mein ghutnon ke bil para howa chore den ge
  19,73,aur jab un logon ke samnay hamari ayatain parhi jati hain to jo kafir hain woh mominoun se kehte hain ke dono fareeq mein se makaan kis ke achay aur mujlisain kis ki behtar hain
  19,74,aur hum ne un se pehlay bohat si ummatain halaak kar dein. woh log ( un se ) thaath aur namood mein kahin achay they
  19,75,keh do ke jo shakhs gumraahi mein para howa hai khuda is ko aahista aahista mohlat diye jata hai. yahan taq ke jab is cheez ko dekh len ge jis ka un se wadakiya jata hai khuwa azaab aur khuwa qayamat. to ( is waqt ) jaan len ge ke makaan kis ka bura hai aur lashkar kis ka kamzor hai
  19,76,aur jo log hadaayat yab hain khuda un ko ziyada hadaayat deta hai. aur naikian jo baqi rehne wali hain woh tumahray perwar-digaar ke siilay ke lehaaz se khoob aur injaam ke aitbaar se behtar hain
  19,77,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jis ne hamari aayton se kufarkiya aur kehnay laga ke ( agar mein az sar e no zindah howa bhi to yahi ) maal aur aulaad mujhe ( wahan ) miley ga
  19,78,kiya is ne ghaib ki khabar palle hai ya khuda ke yahan ( se ) ehad le liya hai ?
  19,79,hargiz nahi. yeh jo kuch kehta hai hum is ko likhte jatay aur is ke liye aahista aahista azaab berhate jatay hain
  19,80,aur jo cheeze yeh batata hai un ke hum waris hon ge aur yeh akela hamaray samnay aeye ga
  19,81,aur un logon ne khuda ke siwa aur mabood bnalye hain taakay woh un ke liye ( mojab izzat o ) madad hon
  19,82,hargiz nahi woh (ma'boodan baatil ) un ki parastish se inkaar karen ge aur un ke dushman (o mukhalif ) hon ge
  19,83,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke hum ne shaitano ko kafiroon par chore rakha hai ke un ko barangekhta karte rehtay hain
  19,84,to tum un par ( azaab ke liye ) jaldi nah karo. aur hum to un ke liye ( din ) shumaar kar rahay hain
  19,85,jis roz hum parhaiz garon ko khuda ke samnay ( bator ) mehman jama karen ge
  19,86,aur gunahgaaron ko dozakh ki taraf pyase haank le jayen ge
  19,87,( to log ) kisi ki sifarish ka ikhtiyar nah rakhen ge magar jis ne khuda se iqraar liya ho
  19,88,aur kehte hain ke khuda beta rakhta hai
  19,89,( aisa kehnay walo yeh to ) tum buri baat ( zabaan par ) laaye ho
  19,90,qareeb hai ke is ( iftira ) se aasman phatt parrin aur zameen shaqq hojaye aur pahar Parah Parah ho kar gir parrin
  19,91,ke unhon ne khuda ke liye beta tajweezkiya
  19,92,aur khuda ko Shayaan nahi ke kisi ko beta banaye
  19,93,tamam shakhs jo asmano aur zameen mein hain sab khuda ke rubaroo bande ho kar ayen ge
  19,94,uss ne un ( sab ) ko ( apne ilm se ) ghair rakha aur ( aik aik ko ) shumaar kar rakha hai
  19,95,aur sab qayamat ke din is ke samnay akailey akailey haazir hon ge
  19,96,aur jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye khuda un ki mohabbat ( makhloqaat ke dil mein ) peda kardey ga
  19,97,( ae paighambar ) hum ne yeh ( quran ) tumhari zabaan mein aasaan ( nazil )kiya hai taakay tum is se parhaiz garon ko khushkhabri pouncha do aur chugralo-own ko dar suna do
  19,98,aur hum ne is se pehlay bohat se garohoon ko halaak kardiya hai. bhala tum un mein se kisi ko dekhte ho ya ( kahin ) un ki bhanak suntay ho
